    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>mango chutney</strong>, <strong>nigella seeds</strong> and <strong>natural</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong> to a small bowl and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>mango yoghurt</strong></p>",
