    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the aubergine has had an initial 20 min, add the <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>smoked paprika </strong>and a splash of <strong>cold water </strong>to the roasting tray<strong> </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for 4-5 min further or until the aubergine is cooked through– this is your<strong> curried aubergine</strong> <strong>&</strong> <strong>onions</strong></p>",
