    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the aubergine is cooking, add the<strong> tortillas</strong> to a separate tray and put the tray in the oven for 2-3 min until warmed through</p><p>Wash the<strong> gem lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred</p><p>Slice the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es] </span></strong>into 6 <span class=\"text-danger\">[12] </span>wedges</p>",
