    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top half of each <strong>warmed tortilla</strong> with the <strong>pilau rice</strong>, <strong>curried aubergine</strong> <strong>&</strong> <strong>onions</strong>, <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>and <strong>tomato wedges</strong></p><p>Dollop the <strong>mango yoghurt</strong> over the top</p><p>Tip: Go light on the filling on your first one so that you don't overfill the burritos!</p>",
